Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:44.55,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Though I respect your skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:49.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I never once thought that you were stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:05.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You helped me get back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san, your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing you in the last round, Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be much stronger than I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call Touya 2dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.83,Background,,0,0,0,,Black is a Korean Kenkyuusei Hong Su-Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou Hikaru is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.05,Background,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.93,Background,,0,0,0,,White is Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is Shindou's strength right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Three weeks... isn't going to be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:07.25,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(345,115)}The Forty-Second Match
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:07.25,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}The First One to Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:13.09,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\fad(542,542)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,355)}Eighteenth Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.45,Background,,0,0,0,,Komiya and Adachi were both at five\Nlosses, but Komiya just beat Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.04,Background,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The top five have all won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won today but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Six losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the end of the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'm hanging off of the cliff\Nby one hand since I'm at seven losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not out of it just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Later Tsubaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:00.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's become something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I, and Komiya and Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us have played against the top five yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have a chance if we can beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford any more losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:24.54,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}The Twentieth Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please start your clocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Ochi 19 Wins 1 Loss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:52.10,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Waya 18 Wins 2 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.52,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Shindou 17 Wins 3 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.82,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Isumi 17 Wins 3 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.20,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Honda 17 Wins 3 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.57,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Komiya 15 Wins 5 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.99,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Adachi 14 Wins 6 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.33,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Katagiri 14 Wins 6 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.75,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(417,417)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}Tsubaki 13 Wins 7 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:13.42,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(1251,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}The Twenty-First Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nase! You beat Honda!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I played a great game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you could have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I can play like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I can't give up on becoming a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:00.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,You played well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,It was a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The top five won't fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.39,Thinking,,0,0,0,,They refuse to fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So... this is the end for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:23.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Last year, Touya Akira was far ahead of everyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:27.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,so we had to compete harder\Nfor the two remaining spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What will happen next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have turned around since the preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to try it at least once,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,before I reached the final year that\NI am allowed to take the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally lost my grip on the edge of the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:20.71,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me for a ride on my\Nbike awhile ago didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll give you a ride to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:38.40,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\frx342\fry12\frz40\pos(215,176)}Japanese Go Research Center
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.90,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz340\frx20\fry10\pos(421,13)}Go Research Center
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.50,Sai,,0,0,0,,What is it Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.44,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:00.90,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki-san! Slow down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you at three losses right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What did you say!? I cant hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I cant hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:17.77,Background,,0,0,0,,A month between the preliminaries and the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:19.66,Background,,0,0,0,,A month and a half since the finals started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.26,Background,,0,0,0,,You were getting stronger all the while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.26,Background,,0,0,0,,I didn't change at all. That is\Nthe difference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.81,Background,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki-san! I can't hear anything you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're Shindou, Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving my dream of becoming a pro with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.66,Background,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'm leaving my dream\Nof becoming a pro with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride, Tsubaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... what you said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you if you mess up in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Tsubaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of what would happen\Nwhen we first met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.72,Background,,0,0,0,,I told you! This move is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.47,Background,,0,0,0,,There's no way a blunt move like this could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you troubled by the combination\Nof a nobi after a nozoki!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have settled for meeting it with a jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you the same thing just three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even trying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I don't understand why\Nyou're so obsessed over Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, his match against the Korean\NKenkyuusei did surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had an incredible game or two as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how strong you are already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so obsessed over Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an even match I had two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku's Kosumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.61,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And black?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's black?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.75,Background,,0,0,0,,His play seems rather archaic but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.25,Background,,0,0,0,,This person playing black is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His moves assault white's weaknesses viciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This strength is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Who's black!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at his game when he first became an Insei,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I played him during the study sessions too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I resigned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! It's impossible! Two years ago!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.27,Background,,0,0,0,,No one would believe that this black player\Nis Shindou from two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No... that is why I haven't shown\Nanyone this match before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the first person I've shown it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't expect you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this match did indeed happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.70,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}The Twenty-Second Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.70,Background,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay! I won by three and a half moku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,This is your nineteenth win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.97,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(292,334)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(432,360)}Adachi 15 Wins 7 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:24.01,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(292,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(282,360)}Shindou 19 Wins 3 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.90,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(542,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(462,83)}Waya 20 wins 2 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.90,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(542,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(178,360)}Komiya 16 Wins 6 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,Good job in seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.25,Sai,,0,0,0,,Now, black has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.98,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(542,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(180,20)}Honda 18 Wins 4 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.98,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\fad(542,0)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(464,335)}Isumi 18 wins 4 Losses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.43,Background,,0,0,0,,Great! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.91,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm still at four losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.39,Background,,0,0,0,,There is a good chance of a playoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Five matches left. I can still pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.12,Sai,,0,0,0,,Playoff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another round if two people\Nare tied for the third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:12.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A playoff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm in danger of that since I'm at three losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.60,Background,,0,0,0,,That move where Honda broke\Nin decided everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.98,Background,,0,0,0,,It looked as if it went in too deep,\Nbut there was no way to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.15,Background,,0,0,0,,It was a good move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost at least eight moku because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no where else to make it back\Neither since it was the end game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san's failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't failed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.25,0:14:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you lose two more games,\Nthere can be a playoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:04.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Five more matches...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost at the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.02,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\frx10\fry6\frz340\pos(392,52)}Japanese Go Research Center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.02,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,360)}The Twenty-Fifth Match of the Pro Exam Finals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.10,Background,,0,0,0,,Congratulations Ochi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose the last two matches, your win\Ntoday has guaranteed that you will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you nervous when you were playing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get overzealous when\Nyou were trying to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told me that if I set an\Neven higher goal for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,passing the exam will happen on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A higher goal than passing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of goal is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to beat Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun? Didn't you beat him\Nduring the Insei study sessions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou has changed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He has grown very rapidly but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well anyways, congratulations on passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck with the rest of your matches too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just accept my congratulations\Nas they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How was your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I won, but I'm not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou is still at three losses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and Isumi-san and Honda-san\Nare still at four losses too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The top five have all won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I guess it doesn't matter to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, you'll be playing Shindou next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm at two losses. I'll pass if I\Nbeat Shindou, who's at three losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, you'll just be watching us\Nfrom above without a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I do care about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing Shindou in the last round.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a throwaway match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be the most important match\Nfor me, out of the entire pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you always think so highly of Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.46,Background,,0,0,0,,I want to find out Shindou's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.56,Background,,0,0,0,,His mysterious strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.28,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to your match\Nagainst Shindou. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Later then, Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.73,Memory,,0,0,0,,This is the Shindou that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't know unless I play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But, I won't lose... I don't want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Not to someone like Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.10,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay, I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go to sleep after another game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.78,Background,,0,0,0,,Seriously!? Is he playing a game!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him since last summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Why are you using\Nthe name Sai!? You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:03.21,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't use Sai's name! He's a legend on the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I mistake Shindou for Sai's student once?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.64,Memory,,0,0,0,,Zelda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.13,Memory,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you said that you were an Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.46,Memory,,0,0,0,,So Waya, you're Zelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.37,Memory,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.70,Memory,,0,0,0,,Why do you know about a conversation\Nbetween Sai and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.30,Memory,,0,0,0,,Could it be he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:37.35,Memory,,0,0,0,,Shindou is... Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.87,Memory,,0,0,0,,It can't be... that's....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His mysterious strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win and pass the pro exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing Waya next...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember? What he said to\Nme the first time I played him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I just made it up to first class?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.91,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.51,Memory,,0,0,0,,It was a good game, Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.73,Memory,,0,0,0,,The opening was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.39,Memory,,0,0,0,,You might get good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.48,Memory,,0,0,0,,As good as Sai one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I started working harder\Nthanks to what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.18,Sai,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to win!
