Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cover maxims today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a maxim is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&HF622F5&\4c&HF622F5&\bord2\shad1\pos(564,390)}Mai
