Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:21.23,Note,,0,0,0,,[Money for a cat is a Japanese expression (or maxim)\Nthat means, "Just like the way giving money to\Na cat is useless, this and that is also useless."]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Money for a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! The thing is, there are maxims for Go too.
