Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at the Go board.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a tsumego where white\Ndies if black goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is a maxim that states, "The\Ncenter is key with a mirror image."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(417,417)\3c&H0D9117&\4c&H0D9117&\bord2\shad1\pos(110,335)}The maxim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(417,417)\3c&HDB00D4&\4c&HDB00D4&\bord2\shad1\pos(320,385)}"The center is key with a mirror image" {\3c&H0D9117&\4c&H0D9117&}is the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to try it Yuuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do Mai-chan, if I go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, even if I take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it back, it's an utegaeshi shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There will only be one eye if you play there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I play here... you can just play\Nhere, and it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(417,417)\3c&H0B8B16&\4c&H0B8B16&\bord2\shad1\pos(320,308)}The maxim states that, when both sides look the\Nsame the center tends to become the key spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The center was the critical spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cover maxims again next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H08B709&\4c&H08B709&\bord2\shad1\pos(320,358)}Maxims again next week. {\3c&H1100ED&\4c&H1100ED&}To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.05,0:22:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The way for black to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! If this black cluster lives, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kill this black cluster, I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I live?
